title: Should Spool adopt the following changes to the LBP?
body:
Should Spool DAO adopt an Addendum to the SPOOL token LBP vote located here: https://snapshot.org/#/prespool.eth/proposal/QmRRPX9rCoF8tXr51Qn63VpQw78QS96t6Ej5UXs6zRpNqR

Changes to the LBP: 
Change the Date of the LBP to October 7, 2021. 

The reason for this delay being that SPOOL should launch with as much token utillity as possible, and we'd like to shorten the gap between token-on-market & token-utillity. 

Update the token amount supplied in the LBP from 10,500 SPOOL (5% of the total supply) to match the new supply when it is finalized in the vote "Increase the supply of SPOOOL to X num"? (If the total supply changes to 210,000,000 SPOOL, then 10,500,000 SPOOL will be supplied for the LBP)

The "Increase the supply of SPOOOL to X num" vote can be found here:
https://snapshot.org/#/prespool.eth/proposal/QmfMnNRTio1e7rKxGk5P6Tg5o9N7gWDBYbrKvP9dxkjbqJ

By passing a YES on this vote, the SPOOL token LBP will be scheduled with the updated details above.
author: 0x33D4523D28d16CE13937903103fb9d3369c9136d
